File: internal/client/commands/root.go
Package: commands
Role: CLI Root Orchestrator
Purpose: Constructs primary execution tree structure. Sets global runtime constraints, PersistentPreRunE lifecycle container boostrapping pipelines, and automated cleanup steps.

