func NewRootCommand(v *viper.Viper) (*cobra.Command, error). Purpose: composition layer. Allocates core layout, hooks PersistentPreRunE and PersistentPostRunE handlers, and binds dynamic flags to target Viper settings nodes. Errors: failure on flag map operations.

